import React, {useState, useContext} from 'react'
import {GlobalState} from '../../GlobalState'
import Slide01 from './imgs/slide-01.jpg'

function Slide(){
    const value = useContext(GlobalState)
    return(
        <slide>
            <Carousel itemsToShow={1}>
                <Item>1</Item>
                <Item>2</Item>
                <Item>3</Item>
                <Item>4</Item>
                <Item>5</Item>
                <Item>6</Item>
            </Carousel>
        </slide>
    )
}

export default Slide
